<div style="background: var(--mn-dark); padding: 48px 52px 44px;">
  <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 36px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px;">
    <img src="<%= relative_url '/images/saulto-logo.png' %>" alt="Saulto" style="height: 26px; filter: brightness(0) invert(1) opacity(0.85);" />
    <span style="font-family: var(--mn-sans); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">
      Confidential
    </span>
  </div>
  <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
    <span style="font-family: var(--mn-sans); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">
      Morris National
    </span>
    <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); font-size: 11px;">&middot;</span>
    <span style="font-family: var(--mn-sans); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #C9A462; background: rgba(201,164,98,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(201,164,98,0.3); border-radius: 100px; padding: 3px 10px;">
      Annual Growth Scenario
    </span>
  </div>
  <h1 style="font-family: var(--mn-serif); font-size: 38px; font-weight: 500; color: #fff; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 18px;">
    How Saulto would protect Morris National's annual goal
  </h1>
  <p style="font-family: var(--mn-sans); font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; max-width: 520px;">
    A scenario showing how Saulto tracks the probability of hitting Morris National's annual goal, catches what threatens it, and tells you exactly what to do before it becomes a problem you are explaining.
  </p>
</div>
